msgid "Optional:"
msgstr "可选："

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md 8ef0684970214306b4387cb8f1bce47a
msgid "**AI API Key**"
msgstr "**AI API 密钥**"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md 03b823c120594f94b29cc2f9fa8f2aa7
msgid "At least one (OpenAI or Anthropic) for AI chat and note generation"
msgstr "AI 对话和笔记生成至少需要一个（OpenAI 或 Anthropic）"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md 8efe2710d84f479aae93b2e469e240d9
msgid "**GitHub Token**"
msgstr "**GitHub Token**"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md 3c3b839c0fa74896a3056d32274364aa
msgid "For cloning/pulling private repositories"
msgstr "用于克隆/拉取私有仓库"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:22 6e0d7211164140faa8fa08ae7c71d1a1
msgid "Step 1: Clone the Repository"
msgstr "步骤 1：克隆仓库"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:29 81162176e26e408b9809cae4f7879ddd
msgid "Step 2: Install Dependencies"
msgstr "步骤 2：安装依赖"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:35 19a41a1fa9be4957bcac3c4ac871c8c8
msgid ""
"This installs all required Node.js packages including Next.js, the AI "
"SDK, database drivers, and UI components."
msgstr "这将安装所有必需的 Node.js 包，包括 Next.js、AI SDK、数据库驱动程序和 UI 组件。"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:37 82d05d6f5db04ef2bde405bb736a04c3
msgid "Step 3: Configure Environment Variables"
msgstr "步骤 3：配置环境变量"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:39 95132e9fcf3e4da5b2690af85ca1fc38
msgid "Copy the example environment file and edit it:"
msgstr "复制示例环境文件并进行编辑："

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:45 4f03eb8962bb4ab6ae197870438b9909
msgid "Edit `.env.local` with your configuration:"
msgstr "使用您的配置编辑 `.env.local`："

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:58 8f6d5c1b3c724eec970571124dfe00b8
msgid ""
"See [Environment Variables](environment-variables.md) for a complete "
"reference of all available options."
msgstr "请参阅[环境变量](environment-variables.md)获取所有可用选项的完整参考。"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:60 58273984ed7a45a79bd75780979447a8
msgid "Step 4: Create Workspace Directories"
msgstr "步骤 4：创建工作空间目录"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:62 b7bf049ded6f423d8a0a901647726f7a
msgid ""
"Ensure the directories specified in `WORKSPACE_ROOTS` exist on your "
"system:"
msgstr "确保系统中存在 `WORKSPACE_ROOTS` 指定的目录："

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:74 bcc68509643d4dd0a82fb5d0ead53b06
msgid ""
"The application will **not** automatically create these directories. They"
" must exist before starting the server."
msgstr "应用程序**不会**自动创建这些目录。在启动服务器之前，这些目录必须已经存在。"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:77 ac7d946abd28483f877d03376e3420de
msgid "Step 5: Initialize the Database"
msgstr "步骤 5：初始化数据库"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:79 e7cbb466f80e44fd8e8b367c9ed38dfc
msgid "Run the database migration to create the SQLite database:"
msgstr "运行数据库迁移以创建 SQLite 数据库："

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:85 4dc8f4f4458a4056a601887d916fc621
msgid ""
"This creates the database file at `./data/innoclaw.db` with all "
"required tables."
msgstr "这将在 `./data/innoclaw.db` 创建包含所有必需表的数据库文件。"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:87 279315102f4740e9b4fdf7ad5a21f964
msgid "Step 6: Start the Development Server"
msgstr "步骤 6：启动开发服务器"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:93 fe80a682196548b0a566cfe0d4eddb3a
msgid ""
"Open your browser and navigate to **http://localhost:3000** to start "
"using InnoClaw."
msgstr "打开浏览器并访问 **http://localhost:3000** 即可开始使用 InnoClaw。"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:95 a3e8372124c140519ac535b368b7d8bd
msgid "Verifying Your Setup"
msgstr "验证安装"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:97 57bdaefe304a4030b5381c9f5989a971
msgid "After starting the server, you should be able to:"
msgstr "启动服务器后，您应该能够："

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:99 042f4f0383a4428c8de040233dc445d0
msgid "See the workspace list on the home page"
msgstr "在首页看到工作空间列表"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:100 6207b35a73e847e88dd6bb329940ed4f
msgid "Create a new workspace from one of your configured root directories"
msgstr "从已配置的根目录之一创建新的工作空间"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:101 9d449e72bd26495fbb01a1846a647231
msgid "Browse and manage files in the workspace"
msgstr "在工作空间中浏览和管理文件"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:102 9bc6dc040e2c42cda1775bf6995f5399
msgid ""
"If an API key is configured, chat with AI about your files (after "
"clicking \"Sync\")"
msgstr "如果已配置 API 密钥，可以就您的文件与 AI 进行对话（点击\"同步\"后）"

#: ../../getting-started/installation.md:105 a305793d1b2140dbb308f9dbe4ec7f33
msgid ""
"If you don't configure any API keys, workspace management, file browsing,"
" uploading, editing, and GitHub cloning features will still work. Only AI"
" chat and note generation will be disabled."
msgstr ""
"如果您未配置任何 API 密钥，工作空间管理、文件浏览、上传、编辑和 GitHub 克隆功能仍然可用。只有 AI "
"对话和笔记生成功能会被禁用。"
